Name: Agent Focus: Jane
Desc: Use it to obtain the Agent or unlock the Agent's Mindscapes.
Desc2:
Snapshots from Jane's daily life and from in combat, recording important moments before and after he became an Agent. These images also provide insights into his fighting style and favorite weapons, helping to better understand her strengths.

A charming lady in an evening dress, a dashing biker on a motorcycle, an elegant cellist on stage... Hmm, did Jane take all these photos? But there's something...
